Amarachi Nwosu (a mụrụ na 29 Septemba 1994) bụ onye Naijiria-Amerika na-ese foto onye, onye na-ese ihe na-ahụ anya, onye na-ese ihe nkiri, onye odee akwụkwọ na ọkàa okwu dabere na New York City ugbu a

Ọ bụkwa ya bụ onye chọọụtara Melanin Unscripted,  usoro ihe okike na ụlọ ọrụ nke ebumnobi ya bụ ịkwatu echiche efu na ime ka ahịrị omenala ghara ime ka ọ pụta ìhè site n'ikpughe njirimara na omenala dị mgbagwoju anya gburugburu ụwa

Akwụkwọ akụkọ mpụta mbụ ya "Black in Tokyo  " ewepụtara na International Center of Photography na ICP Museum, New York City na 2017 ma gosikwa ihe nkiri ahụ na Tokyo, Japan na Ultra Super New Gallery na Harajuku
A mụnyere n'ezinaụlọ nne na nna bụ ndị Naịjiria nwere nketa Igbo, Itsekiri na Ghana,  Amarachi toro na Washington DC wee bie ụfọdụ ndụ nwata ya na Port Harcourt, Nigeria na New York City

Nwosu gara ụlọ akwụkwọ na Temple University dị na Filadelfia mana ọ kwagara Tokyo n'ime afọ nta ya ka o nwetachara akwụkwọ mmụta isii ka ọ nwee ike ịgụ akwụkwọ otu afọ na mba ofesi dị ka nwa akwụkwọ mba ofesi ebe o nwetara akara ugo mmụta na International Communications

Ọ laghachiri n'ụlọ akwụkwọ na States ka ọ gụchaa ogo ya wee laghachi na Tokyo ịmụta Japanese na-arụ ọrụ dị ka ihe oge nile ihe okike ebe ọ bụ akụkụ nke mmalite nke Highsnobiety na Japan na ndị ahịa dị ka Beats na Sony Music Japan
Ntinye aka Nwosu na omenala gbagoro n'ọrụ dị iche iche site na egwu, ejiji, egwuregwu na mmetụta ọha mmadụ
Ọrụ ya na-elekwasị anya n'ijikota oghere ndị a site na ịkọ akụkọ ọhụụ na mmetụta obodo
Ọ gbara akụkọ ejiji, 'Sankofa' na Cape Coast Castle na Ghana maka Vogue
Onye na-eme ihe ike, Malala Yousafzai bụ onye mmeri Nobel nke ọdụdụ nyere ya iwu ka ọ depụta nleta ya na Tokyo na 2019

Ọnụ ọgụgụ ndị ọzọ dị ike ọ na-ekpuchi ma gbagburu gụnyere supermodel Naomi Campbell n'oge njem ya na Lagos, Nigeria,   Ebonee Davis  ma durukwa obere ihe nkiri na ike ụmụ nwanyị na egwuregwu maka ụlọ ọrụ dị ka Nike na Nigeria
Nwosu etinyela aka n'ịkwanye Afrobeats na ụda afrofusion dị ka onye na-ese ihe nkiri, onye nta akụkọ egwu, onye nduzi ihe okike na njikwa ika
She has work with artists like Mr Eazi, Yxng Bane, Nonso Amadi, Odunsi The Engine, Santi, Kwesi Arthur and Tobi Lou
Ọ rụkwara ọrụ dị ka onye na-ese ihe nlegharị anya maka Childish Gambino n'oge njem 2018 'Nke a bụ America'

N'afọ 2018, o duziri mmalite nke Budweiser na Nigeria site na ikpo okwu Budx ha  site n'ịkwado ihe ngosi ebe obibi maka onye na-ede akwụkwọ Hip Hop nke Naijiria-American Chi Modu n'ime ikpo okwu Melanin ya edeghị ede dị ka ụzọ isi mechie oge ọla edo nke Hip Hop na America
na oghere Hip Hop dị ugbu a na Nigeria
Ihe omume a bụ ihe ngosi ụbọchị abụọ, ogbako, panel, concert na oriri

Ọ bụkwa ya na-ahụ maka ịchịkọta egwu na omenala ndị ntorobịa n'ebe ndị dị ka Tokyo ebe ọ gbara ihe mbụ maka The Fader na-akọwapụta ihe nkiri egwu nke oge a na Tokyo, Japan  ma gbaa nwanyị Africa mbụ pụtara na ibe Instagram Adidas Tokyo dị ka ụzọ isi pụta ìhè iche iche na Japan.
Amarachi ejirila olu ya na soshal midia metụta ọha mmadụ ma kpalie ụmụ agbọghọ na-eto eto gburugburu ụwa

N'afọ 2017,  ọ na-ekwu okwu nke ukwuu n'ịkpọsa mkpesa doro anya na ntinye omenala nke mbipụta ndị Africa  site n'aka onye mmepụta Britain, Stella McCartney n'oge ngosi ya na Paris Fashion Week na saịtị micro-blogging, Twitter na-ewe iwe na mgbasa ozi mgbasa ozi
OkayAfrica kpọrọ ya "Cultural Colonialism"  na na tweet viral, ọ kwara arịrị maka iji ụdị Africa nke ika a "ma na-eji naanị otu ụdị Africa n'okporo ụzọ ụgbọ elu ya"
N'agbanyeghị nnukwu azụghachi azụ ahụ, McCartney jụrụ ịrịọ mgbaghara wee wepụta nkwupụta nye Fashionista nke nyere otuto akwa akwa, Vlisco na Netherlands karịa ụmụ nwanyị Africa.
“Mbipụta ndị a bụ maka ime mmemme nka akwa pụrụ iche, omenala ya na ikpughe ihe nketa ya
Anyị na Vlisco na Netherlands rụpụtara mbipụta ndị a, ụlọ ọrụ na-ekepụta akwa ezigbo Dutch Wax pụrụ iche na Holland kemgbe 1846 ma na-enyere aka idobe ihe nketa ya
o dere

Mgbe Rihanna kwuputara ahịrị ejiji okomoko ya na mmekorita ya na LVMH Moët Hennessy Louis Vuitton maka 2019, Amarachi Nwosu bụ otu n'ime ndị isi ihe na-eme ihe na-eji ikpo okwu ha too onye na-agụ egwú pop
Na-akpọ Rihanna "akara ngosi zuru oke" nke "ike ga-enwe mmetụta maka ọgbọ na-abịa"
